	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=154268><span id= >Selarea</span></a><br><span id=notbold>72 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.60]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>My enchanter keeps this in her bag at all times for two reasons.<br><br>1. To cast Clarity on the characters not high enough for C2. Kind of unnecessary after 59 though since you can group C2 or cast KEI at 60 and still get noobs in that. If you don't wanna waste your time to group up and mana to cast those spells, this will do the trick. <br><br>2. Corpse runs. Whenever my enchanter is unfortunate enough to have to die, after getting a rez, click this and helps me regain my mana back a little quicker to get enough mana to cast a better spell. Saves me a little bit of med time. </p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
